“A Portrait of the” and “Tadd Myers” is [Brothers Regular Alternates](http://web.archive.org/web/20090503110213/http:/new.myfonts.com/fonts/emigre/brothers/), “A Collection by” is the matching italics (not sure if Alternate or not).  
I’m sure Lex will get the rest :-)

OK, looks like “Craftsman” is Trade Gothic.
